snippet: Nearly 600 U.S. soldiers accompanied by tanks and other vehicles will arrive in Poland and the Baltic states at the weekend for military exercises, the Polish defense ministry said on Friday....

headline.print_headline: Nearly 600 U.S. Soldiers With Tanks to Arrive in Poland, Baltics
headline.main: Nearly 600 U.S. Soldiers With Tanks to Arrive in Poland, Baltics

lead_paragraph: Nearly 600 U.S. soldiers accompanied by tanks and other vehicles will arrive in Poland and the Baltic states at the weekend for military exercises, the Polish defense ministry said on Friday.
